---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Prescription Glasses in Tijuana | Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río"
  description="Wide selection of frames and prescription glasses in Tijuana. Tailored to your prescription with an adaptation guarantee. Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río."
  alternates={[
    { hreflang: "en", href: "https://www.jarmar.com/en/tijuana/prescription-glasses/" },
    { hreflang: "es", href: "https://www.jarmar.com/tijuana/lentes-graduados/" },
    { hreflang: "x-default", href: "https://www.jarmar.com/tijuana/lentes-graduados/" }
  ]}
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #071A3E;
      --surface: #0D2B6B;
      --accent: #3A8FE0;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 100px 20px 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(58,143,224,0.2);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .section:nth-child(even) { background: #f7f9fc; }
    .section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title span { color: var(--accent); }
    .section-sub { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }

    .tipos-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .tipo-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.25); border-radius: 18px; padding: 28px 24px; }
    .tipo-card h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .tipo-card p { color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; }
    .tipo-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }

    .materiales { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .mat-chip { background: var(--surface); color: #fff; border-radius: 100px; padding: 10px 22px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }

    .garantia-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%);
      color: #fff; border-radius: 24px; padding: 44px 40px; text-align: center;
    }
    .garantia-box h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .garantia-box p { font-size: 1.05rem; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 28px; }

    .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 28px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">Optical · Tijuana</span>
      <h1>Prescription Glasses<br>in <span>Tijuana</span></h1>
      <p>Wide selection of frames and premium lenses, tailored exactly to your prescription. From single vision to high-definition progressives.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+prescription+glasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Explore options →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Types of <span>prescription lenses</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We carry all vision solutions for every lifestyle and optical need.</p>
      <div class="tipos-grid">
        <div class="tipo-card">
          <span class="tipo-icon">👁️</span>
          <h4>Single Vision</h4>
          <p>For myopia, hyperopia, or astigmatism. One prescription for the distance you need most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo-card">
          <span class="tipo-icon">🔍</span>
          <h4>Bifocals</h4>
          <p>Two vision zones in one lens: far and near. Ideal for presbyopia combined with another correction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo-card">
          <span class="tipo-icon">✨</span>
          <h4>Progressives</h4>
          <p>Smooth transition from far to intermediate to near. No visible line — the most natural presbyopia solution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo-card">
          <span class="tipo-icon">💻</span>
          <h4>Occupational</h4>
          <p>Designed for office work and screen use. Optimizes the intermediate and near vision zones.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Materials and <span>treatments</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We offer lenses in the best technologies available so your visual experience is optimal from day one.</p>
      <div class="materiales">
        <span class="mat-chip">Polycarbonate</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Trivex</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Organic 1.67</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Organic 1.74</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Anti-reflective AR</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">UV400 filter</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Photochromic</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Blue light filter</span>
        <span class="mat-chip">Hydrophobic coating</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Adaptation <span>guarantee</span></h2>
      <div class="garantia-box">
        <h3>If your lenses don't feel right, we fix them</h3>
        <p>At Ópticas Jarmar we offer an adaptation guarantee on all prescription glasses. If during the adaptation period something doesn't feel right, we review your case at no extra cost until we find the perfect solution for you.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+prescription+glasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">Ask about the guarantee</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Find your perfect glasses in Tijuana</h2>
      <p>Visit us at Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río or message us on WhatsApp for personalized advice.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+prescription+glasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="/en/tijuana/" class="back-link">← Back to Tijuana</a>
</BaseLayout>
